OL,6,FSure customers in the Channel Islands
OL,7,Fwill be unable to top up their mobile
OL,8,Fphones for four days, from tomorrow,
OL,9,Fwhile the company brings Airtel users
OL,10,Finto their systems.
OL,12,FSure says there will be no change to
OL,13,Fother mobile, broadband and landline
OL,14,Fservices during this period.
