OL,6,FThe firm took over rival Airtel last
OL,7,FNovember after States of Guernsey
OL,8,Fvoted to temporarily suspend local
OL,9,Fcompetition law to allow it a month
OL,10,Fearlier, with the Jersey Competition
OL,11,FRegulatory Authority (JCRA) having
OL,12,Fapproved it in August 2024.
OL,14,FSure says all Airtel customers will be
OL,15,F'fully migrated' to their systems by
OL,16,FWednesday (24 September).
OL,18,FIn a statement, Simon Baldwin, Sure's
OL,19,FChief Commercial Officer, said: "We've
OL,20,Fcommunicated directly with
